该剧是歌颂公安警察执法为民的献礼剧。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sohu.com/20080921/n259664702.shtml |title=赵恒煊《警中英雄》出演公安局长 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |date=2008-09-21 |work=搜狐 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211644/http://news.sohu.com/20080921/n259664702.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>被誉为塑造了新时代的警察形象。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2009-03-02/10252397767.shtml |title=《警中英雄》塑造新时代的“警察偶像” |accessdate=2013-07-29|date=2009-03-02 |work=新浪}}</ref>

